## Directory structure for projects:

|--Project
|  |
|  |--include
|  |  |--main.h
|  |--lib
|  |  |--gpio
|  |  |--rcc
|  |  |--usart
|  |--src
|  |  |--main.c

### Important Points
- `src` should contain application level source files
- `include` should contain application level header files
- `lib` should contain peripheral libraries, device drivers, etc.